[[File:Diamond detail.png|left|130px]]
A '''Diamond''' is a white [[Gems|gem]] used in [[Crafting]] and [[Fletching]]. Diamonds can be cut from [[uncut diamond]]s with level 43 Crafting by using a [[chisel]], granting 107.5 experience. When used with a [[furnace]] and [[jewellery]] [[mould]], they can be used to make diamond jewellery.

One diamond is required to enter the [[Zanaris]] marketplace.

